body_html: @giuliohome please visit Tensorflowsharp. We are using the latest window dll contributed by this group C API. We need more people to port python tensorflow examples/tutorials codes to .NET. We have tested Xamarin Workbook (Jupiter notebook alternative) to support the porting and sharing of .NET example tensorflow codes
